column2: SELECT m.RA AS ra1, m.DEC AS dec1, stack.ra AS ra, stack.dec AS dec, stack.cModelMag_u AS cModelMag_u, stack.cModelMagErr_u AS cModelMagErr_u, stack.cModelMag_g AS cModelMag_g, stack.cModelMagErr_g AS cModelMagErr_g, stack.cModelMag_r AS cModelMag_r, stack.cModelMagErr_r AS cModelMagErr_r, stack.cModelMag_i AS cModelMag_i, stack.cModelMagErr_i AS cModelMagErr_i, stack.cModelMag_z AS cModelMag_z, stack.cModelMagErr_z AS cModelMagErr_z, stack.extinction_u AS extinction_u, stack.extinction_g AS extinction_g, stack.extinction_r AS extinction_r, stack.extinction_i AS extinction_i, stack.extinction_z AS extinction_z FROM MyDB.wise_clean AS m OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll AS stack ON n.objid = stack.objID into MyDB.wise_cModelMag
